	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />@estlib:  I really like the colors and style.  What is it for?<br /><br />@jayminer:  The entire game would have to be re-designed to work optimally on the NES.  Flicker is one of the hard limits of the NES, and there's only so much you can do to work around it.  Maybe flicker could just be standard with the port, preferably the 'blink in and out of existence' kind like Recca's, not the 'temporarily not draw a sprite until it is out of the line' like Bubble Bobble's.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
